'''番茄汁'''是以[[番茄|番茄]]製成的[[果汁|果汁]]，一般作为[[饮料|饮料]]服用，也可作为[[血玛丽|血玛丽]]、{{tsl|en|Michelada}}等[[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]的配料。

== 历史 ==
番茄汁最早于1917年由{{#property:P61}}在[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]]的[[弗倫奇利克溫泉酒店|弗倫奇利克溫泉酒店]]作为饮料提供。当时他用尽了橙汁，需要找个替换。他对压碎的番茄、糖以及独家酱料的特别组合随着[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]商人们的口口相传很快就大获成功。<ref>Anne Hattes. "Tomato Juice". ''Relish'', Aug. 2009.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.frenchlick.com/aboutus/history/flsh |title=History {{!}} French Lick Springs Hotel {{!}} French Lick Resort<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522124458/http://www.frenchlick.com/aboutus/history/flsh |dead-url=no }}</ref>随着番茄汁的流行，商人们也越来越成功。

== 生产 ==
大部分商业量产的番茄汁都额外加[[食用盐|食用盐]]，有时还会加入[[洋葱粉|洋葱粉]]、[[大蒜粉|大蒜粉]]等[[香辛料|香辛料]]。在[[美国|美国]]，[[大量生產|大量生產]]的番茄汁于1920年代上市，几年内就成为流行的[[早餐|早餐]]饮品。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CecCHiI95dYC&pg=PA122&dq=breakfast,+tomato+juice&hl=en&sa=X&ei=xvxjUc3cI-qpiQLS34DYAQ&ved=0CFMQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=breakfast%2C%20tomato%20juice&f=false |title=Nineteen Twenties - Kathleen Morgan Drowne, Patrick Huber<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511213137/https://books.google.com/books?id=CecCHiI95dYC&pg=PA122&dq=breakfast,+tomato+juice&hl=en&sa=X&ei=xvxjUc3cI-qpiQLS34DYAQ&ved=0CFMQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=breakfast%2C%20tomato%20juice&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>按加拿大法律，番茄汁必须由整顆番茄製成；而美国则大多使用番茄泥。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/heinz-deal-to-save-hundreds-of-jobs-at-leamington-plant-1.2552388 |title=Heinz deal to save hundreds of jobs at Leamington plant - Windsor - CBC News<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015930/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/windsor/heinz-deal-to-save-hundreds-of-jobs-at-leamington-plant-1.2552388 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

